WEBVTT

1
00:07:40.100 --> 00:07:41.740 
我也讨厌这一切
I hate this, too!

2
00:07:41.770 --> 00:07:43.500 
特别讨厌
I hate this!

3
00:07:43.540 --> 00:07:46.410 
我讨厌我不得不取消所有的手术
I hate that I've had to cancel all of my surgeries!

4
00:07:46.440 --> 00:07:48.110 
我讨厌人们死去
I hate that people are dying

5
00:07:48.140 --> 00:07:50.680 
就因为他们无法得到医疗救治
because they don't have access to healthcare!

6
00:07:50.750 --> 00:07:54.320 
我讨厌把一整天花在视频会议上
I hate that my entire day is spent on a computer conference!

7
00:07:54.380 --> 00:07:55.520 
开会 开个屁
Conference, conference!

8
00:07:55.550 --> 00:07:59.450 
我讨厌不管我们怎么做 人们都在死去
And I hate that everyone is dying no matter what we do!

9
00:07:59.490 --> 00:08:01.660 
老天 我讨厌那么多人都死去
Lord, I hate that everyone is dying!

10
00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:02.890 
我讨厌自己无能为力
I hate that I can't fix it!

11
00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:04.830 
我才讨厌自己无能为力
I hate that I can't fix this!

